'''多爾威澤蘭城堡'''（{{lang-cy|Castell Dolwyddelan}}、{{IPA-cy|kastɛɬ dɔlwɪð'ɛlan}}；{{lang-en|Dolwyddelan Castle}}、{{IPAc-en|d|ɒ|l|w|ɪ|ð|'|ɛ|l|æ|n|}}、{{respell|dol|with|EL|an}}）是位於[[英國|英國]][[威爾斯|威爾斯]]的一座城堡，靠近[[北威爾斯|北威爾斯]][[康威郡自治市|康威郡自治市]]的{{link-en|多爾威澤蘭|Dolwyddelan}}。這座城堡被認為由[[盧埃林大帝|盧埃林大帝]]修建於13世紀。城堡最初僅有一座兩層高的塔樓，第二座塔樓則修建於13世紀後期；在15世紀後期的維修中，第一座塔樓增建了第三層。

==建築==
這座城堡主要使用當地的砂礫和石板瓦礫修建，是[[格溫內斯王國|格溫內斯王國]]王子在[[史諾多尼亞|史諾多尼亞]]的據點之一<ref name="Sutton">{{cite book |title= The Sutton Companion to Castles |url= https://archive.org/details/suttoncompaniont0000fria_e3c5 |author= Stephen Friar |publisher= Sutton Publishing |isbn= 0750927445 |year= 2003}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |title= Mediaeval Castles in North Wales |author= Ernest Neaverson |year= 1947 |publisher= The University Press of Liverpool |pages= 31–33}}</ref>。雖然缺乏明確的修建日期記錄，但多認為長方形兩層高塔樓修建於13世紀初期<ref name="Sutton"/><ref name="sign">{{cite sign |title= Dolwyddelan Castle |type= Sign inside castle |location= Dolwyddelan Castle |publisher=CADW}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |title= Wandering in North Wales |author= Thomas Roscoe |year= 1844}}</ref>。這座塔樓的一層包括一個帶有壁爐的主要房間，以及通往地下室入口的活動門<ref>{{cite book |url= https://books.google.com/books?id=fBbNJLEWiLIC&q=dolwyddelan%20castle&pg=PA102 |title= Britain's Medieval Castles |year= 2006 |page= 102 |publisher= Praeger Publishers |isbn= 0275984141 |access-date= 2022-01-11 |archive-date= 2022-01-11 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20220111140006/https://books.google.com/books?id=fBbNJLEWiLIC&q=dolwyddelan%20castle&pg=PA102 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。主塔的入口被一個{{link-en|門廊|porch}}覆蓋<ref name="Kenyon"/>。

第二座兩層塔樓修建於1283年至1284年，由愛德華一世在維修時期添加。這座塔樓通過一個不規則的幕牆和中庭連接，並在1290年至1292年進一步擴建<ref name="Taylor">{{cite book |title= The Welsh Castles of Edward I |author= Arnold Taylor |year= 1986 |publisher= The Hambledon Press |isbn= 0907628710}}</ref><ref name="Kenyon">{{cite book |title= The Medieval Castles of Wales |author= John Kenyon |publisher= The University of Wales Press |isbn= 9780708321805 |year= 2010}}</ref>。第二座塔在頂層有一個壁爐，並可通過內部樓梯到達<ref name="Kenyon"/>。15世紀後期，主塔增建了第三層<ref name="Jenkins">{{cite book |title= Wales: Churches, Houses, Castles |url= https://archive.org/details/waleschurcheshou0000jenk |author= Simon Jenkins |isbn= 978-0-141-02412-7 |year= 2011}}</ref>，總高度因此達到{{convert|12.3|m}}<ref>The Snowdonia Tourism Association. ''The Villages of Snowdon''.</ref>。1848年至1850年期間，{{link-en|雷斯比的威洛比|Baron Willoughby de Eresby}}對城堡進行了大幅修繕，並在此期間增建了[[垛口|垛口]]<ref name="Sutton"/><ref name="sign"/>。

==歷史==
[[File:Dolwyddelan_castle_02402.jpg|thumb]]
這座城堡修建在13世紀初期，最初被作為穿過北威爾斯主要路線的一座哨所使用<ref name="Jenkins"/>。多爾威澤蘭城堡曾被認為是[[盧埃林大帝|盧埃林大帝]]的出生地，但現在主流觀點傾向於他出生在城堡附近小丘上的一座名為Tomen Castell的塔樓，並且由盧埃林大帝建造<ref name="Sutton"/><ref name="Geraint">{{cite book |title= Welsh Castles |author= Geraint Roberts |isbn= 0862435501 |publisher= Y Lolfa |year= 2006}}</ref>。1283年1月18日，英格蘭國王[[愛德華一世|愛德華一世]]在征服威爾斯的最後階段佔領了這座城堡<ref name="Ed">{{cite book |url= https://books.google.com/books?id=Vp2r3xyaDaEC&q=dolwyddelan%20castle&pg=PA195 |title= Edward I |author= Michael Prestwich |year= 1988 |publisher= University of California Press |isbn= 0520062663 |access-date= 2022-01-11 |archive-date= 2022-01-11 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20220111141154/https://books.google.com/books?id=Vp2r3xyaDaEC&q=dolwyddelan%20castle&pg=PA195 |dead-url= no }}</ref>{{rp|194–195}}。有一些歷史學家認為城堡的防御者可能和愛德華一世之間達成了協議，通過談判投降<ref name="Ed"/>{{rp|195}}。 

在1286年之前，有記錄證明英格蘭軍隊曾佔領這座城堡，並對這座城堡進行維修和加固。現仍保留有當時對橋樑和[[水磨|水磨]]的維修記錄<ref name="Taylor" /><ref>{{cite web |url= http://cadw.wales.gov.uk/daysout/dolwyddelan-castle/?lang=en |title= Dolwyddelan Castle |access-date= 28 August 2013 |work= CADW |date= 2011 |archive-date= 2013-09-27 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130927042431/http://cadw.wales.gov.uk/daysout/dolwyddelan-castle/?lang=en |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |url= http://site.ebrary.com/lib/liverpool/docDetail.action?docID=10271718 |title= Plantagenet England 1225–1360 |year= 2005 |author= Prestwich, Michael |page= 155}}</ref>。愛德華時代的駐軍在這裡維持至1290年<ref name="Hull">{{cite book |url= https://books.google.com/books?id=ypUl6iU3zlUC&q=dolwyddelan%20castle&pg=PA122 |title= Great Castles of Britain and Ireland |author= Lise Hull |page= 122 |year= 2008 |publisher= New Holland Publishers |isbn= 9781847731302}}</ref>。

1488年，{{link-en|馬雷杜德·伊凡|Maredudd ap Ifan}}通過租約成為這裡的領主。他在15世紀時增建了建築的上層部分和排水系統<ref>{{cite book |title= The Conwy Valley: Its Long History |author= Michael Senior |year= 1984 |isbn= 0863810357 |publisher= Gwasg Carreg Gwalch |page= 23}}</ref>。19世紀時，{{link-en|雷斯比的威洛比|Baron Willoughby de Eresby}}對城堡進行了修復和部分改建，加蓋了[[垛口|垛口]]<ref name="sign"/>。有記載稱1810年時，城堡雙塔中的一座可能已經倒塌<ref name="arch">{{cite journal |journal= Archaeologia Cambrensis |title= Dolwyddelan Castle |year= 1883 |author= Barnwell, E. L. |volume= 38 |page= 51 |url= https://archive.org/stream/archaeologiacam05moorgoog#page/n66/mode/1up |access-date= 2014-04-09}}</ref>。

1930年開始，城堡由{{link-en|工程部 (英國)|Ministry of Works (United Kingdom)|英國工程部}}保護<ref>{{cite book |title= An Inventory of the Ancient Monuments in Caernarvonshire: I East: the Cantref of Arllechwedd and the Commote of Creuddyn |volume= 1 |year= 1956 |author= The Royal Commission on the Ancient and Historical Monuments of Wales |pages= 80–82 |url= https://books.google.com/books?id=Zy2olxXGPhwC |access-date= 2022-01-11 |archive-date= 2022-01-11 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20220111141153/https://books.google.com/books?id=Zy2olxXGPhwC |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name="Hull"/>。現在多爾威澤蘭城堡由[[威爾斯議會|威爾斯議會]]的歷史環境部門之一的{{link-en|Cadw|Cadw}}保護<ref>{{cite book |title= The Hidden Places of North and Mid Wales |author= Mike Weil |isbn= 1871815568 |page= 84 |publisher= M&M Publishing |year= 1994}}</ref>。

==電影拍攝==
多爾威澤蘭城堡在1980年曾被電影《{{link-en|屠龍記 (1981年電影)|Dragonslayer (1981 film)|屠龍記}}》選為劇中角色尤爾瑞奇（Ulrich）的城堡的外景拍攝地<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.dailypost.co.uk/whats-on/restaurants-bars/dolwyddelan-castle-2865323 |title= Dolwyddelan Castle |date= 2007-09-18 |access-date= 2013-09-02 |work= North Wales Daily Post |archive-date= 2018-12-11 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20181211205319/https://www.dailypost.co.uk/whats-on/restaurants-bars/dolwyddelan-castle-2865323 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。
